query:
SELECT 
  p.id,
  p.productId,
  p.name,
  c.name as categoryName,
  pc.isPrimary
FROM products p
JOIN product_categories pc ON p.id = pc.productId
JOIN categories c ON pc.categoryId = c.id
WHERE c.slug = 'gc-columns'
LIMIT 10;
